### REST Swagger
GET http://127.0.0.1:8089/swagger/rest.json

### XML/SOAP Swagger
GET http://127.0.0.1:8089/swagger/xml.json

### REST API index
GET http://127.0.0.1:8089/api

### REST login as admin
POST http://127.0.0.1:8089/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin_aurora",
  "password": "adminpass1"
}

### REST validate token
GET http://127.0.0.1:8089/api/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### REST admin list products
GET http://127.0.0.1:8089/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### REST admin create product
POST http://127.0.0.1:8089/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "sku": "SKU-REST-1",
  "name": "REST Test Product",
  "price": 77.7,
  "stock": 7
}

### REST admin edit product with custom PUSH
PUSH http://127.0.0.1:8089/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "sku": "SKU-REST-1",
  "price": 88.8,
  "stock": 8
}

### REST admin edit product with Swagger-friendly alias
POST http://127.0.0.1:8089/api/products/push
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "sku": "SKU-REST-1",
  "price": 99.9
}

### REST admin delete product
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8089/api/products?sku=SKU-REST-1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### REST refresh token, intentionally reusable in test mode
POST http://127.0.0.1:8089/api/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refresh_token}}"
}

### REST login as user
POST http://127.0.0.1:8089/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user_apollo",
  "password": "userpass1"
}

### REST user list products
GET http://127.0.0.1:8089/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{user_access_token}}

### REST user forbidden write
POST http://127.0.0.1:8089/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{user_access_token}}

{
  "sku": "SKU-BLOCKED",
  "name": "Blocked Product",
  "price": 1,
  "stock": 1
}

### REST audit
GET http://127.0.0.1:8089/api/audit
